snippet: Pakistani police have found body of a man in the central city of Multan with chained feet, tied hands, and wearing a Guantanamo-style orange jumpsuit....

headline.main: Pakistan's Police Find Body Bearing Marks of IS Execution
headline.print_headline: Pakistan's Police Find Body Bearing Marks of IS Execution

lead_paragraph: Pakistani police have found body of a man in the central city of Multan with chained feet, tied hands, and wearing a Guantanamo-style orange jumpsuit.
